longBusinessSummary: Dalrada Corporation, through its subsidiaries, provides various solutions for businesses and consumers worldwide. The company develops and manages products and services in engineering, manufacturing, and healthcare. It offers various alternative solutions to OEMs through design and manufacturing of component parts that are customized for any specific solution; and heater/chiller units that provide simultaneous heating and cooling without the need for combustion or the burning of fossil fuels. The company also develops health products and services that address the unmet needs of consumers. In addition, it provides end to end product engineering services in various domains, including banking and financial services, telecom, retail, healthcare, manufacturing, legal, and IT infrastructure. Dalrada Corporation was incorporated in 1982 and is based in Escondido, California.
